---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<PageLayout
  title="Warranty — Syvidea"
  description="Warranty information for Syvidea's curated partner workstation options."
>
  <article class="section">
    <div class="container-page max-w-3xl prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert">
      <h1>Warranty</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Syvidea does not manufacture the workstations. Warranty terms are set by the partner brand
        (BOSGAME, PELAND, or BITPC) that produces the specific unit you purchase. This page summarizes
        the general approach. Final warranty terms are confirmed in your written quote.
      </p>

      <h2>What the warranty covers</h2>
      <p>
        Partner brand warranty typically covers defects in materials and workmanship under normal use
        during the warranty period. The specific period (commonly 1 or 2 years) and coverage scope depend
        on the partner brand and the specific model configuration.
      </p>

      <h2>What is not covered</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Damage from accidents, drops, spills, or physical impact</li>
        <li>Damage from unauthorized disassembly or modification</li>
        <li>Damage from use outside the documented operating environment</li>
        <li>Normal wear and tear</li>
        <li>Software issues unrelated to hardware defects</li>
        <li>Consumables and accessories (cables, adapters) unless defective on arrival</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How to make a warranty claim</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Contact us via the contact form with your order number, partner brand, and a description of the issue.</li>
        <li>We work with the partner brand to confirm coverage and next steps.</li>
        <li>Depending on the issue and the partner brand process, we may arrange repair, replacement, or return-to-base service.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Local support vs. shipping back</h2>
      <p>
        Warranty resolution is handled in coordination with the partner brand. For international customers,
        the partner brand's regional support path applies. Shipping costs for warranty service are handled
        per the partner brand's policy and confirmed at claim time.
      </p>

      <h2>Final terms</h2>
      <p>
        The exact warranty terms for your unit are the terms published by the partner brand for the
        specific model and configuration you purchase, as confirmed in your quote. Syvidea helps
        coordinate the claim, but the warranty is ultimately a partner-brand warranty.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</PageLayout>
